{"tid":105942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"詹培忠控《蘋果日報》誹謗勝訴　獲賠10萬元","createTime":"2017-02-03T09:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T15:57:31.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24873b8a1bcb44af47901700797ff0423b89982e","tid":105942,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/photo/bkn-20170203160611501-0203_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170203162243\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170203160611501-0203_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170203162243&h=96266349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n詹培忠(左)控告《蘋果日報》誹謗案獲判勝訴。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員詹培忠於2014年世界盃舉行期間，在電視節目中講及賭波必勝方程式，《蘋果日報》體育版其後於同年7月5日刊登專欄文章，譏笑詹是「傻佬」及「信佢一成都死」。詹指事件涉及誹謗，遂興訟高院控告《蘋果日報》出版商蘋果日報有限公司、時任總編輯張劍虹及專欄作者梁柏堅等被告。<br />\n<br />\n高院今日判詹培忠勝訴，下令《蘋果日報》、時任總編輯張劍虹及涉案專欄作者梁柏堅，需賠償10萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/bkn-20170203160611501-0203_00822_001.html?refer=fn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fbkn-20170203160611501-0203_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dfn2&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e25e0b80\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/bkn-20170203160611501-0203_00822_001.html?refer=fn2</a>"},{"pid":"c2ecd86ba229bc4682b87b1f622fdf9d243bc223","tid":105942,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"下,駛唔駛呀? 條友講D野真係好傻吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05a2d1ca748d449d84e6014414d727f0fc85333","tid":105942,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"頌費都唔只幾多十倍"},{"pid":"cae3dd688b76b8c76d648c1cb7f3002146c29d02","tid":105942,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"講主觀感覺都有罪？<br />\n第時我話人樣衰係咪又可以告我誹謗？"},{"pid":"110cabec001783ed557307151308d99bd1f72578","tid":105942,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:38:44.000Z","msg":"未到16強，已經要懸樑"},{"pid":"7390a865774a9a5e92a1ae6f5b5ad297425b2d1a","tid":105942,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"勝訴即係真啦<br />\n求方程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7689ec4b28d9e9d211eedd64719d63bd84cdc670","tid":105942,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頌費都唔只幾多十倍</blockquote><br />\n佢賭一場牌都只止呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba62b86b67c40a76c41a44dd6be921ba29024993","tid":105942,"uid":32178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講主觀感覺都有罪？<br />\n第時我話人樣衰係咪又可以告我誹謗？</blockquote><br />\n有錢的真係可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d5b657ba3c554561bdc3ff95209a438213dd24","tid":105942,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講主觀感覺都有罪？<br />\n第時我話人樣衰係咪又可以告我誹謗？</blockquote><br />\n有錢同你磨真係可以"},{"pid":"386b948ec2d6490de49dc0ecd0a305fd8d2a4c3a","tid":105942,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"佢既所謂必勝法 其實即係本多終勝法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fd2c91d33bfe4fd7b7e9f40c49ade88a1111f0","tid":105942,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fe6d7b501bbf4123521fe87aa899f57a7d4296","tid":105942,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:27:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都